name: Cascades Springs
overview:
CASCADES Springs inc. specializes in the manufacturing of precision springs, wire forms and custom metal parts, from prototype to production.

Founded in 1976, CASCADES Springs inc is rapidly becoming a national leader in the industry.

The compagny uses its leadership to offer its custmers high-quality products at competitive price.

Always alert to opportunities, CASCADES Springs inc meets customers, increasingly demanding needs with its highly qualified personnel and equipment on the cutting edge of technology.

We work in many industrial sectors, including automobile, electrical, electrical appliance, rail, and military among others.
